  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 28200.0,
      "end_time": 30275.0,
      "text": "This is Shanhua Sugar Refinery."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 30525.0,
      "end_time": 33125.0,
      "text": "There are lots of sugar refineries in Taiwan."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 33375.0,
      "end_time": 35167.0,
      "text": "But do you know why in Shanhua?"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 35350.0,
      "end_time": 38500.0,
      "text": "And besides the sugar, what products do they make now?"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 38800.0,
      "end_time": 42192.0,
      "text": "And what we can find only in Shanhua Sugar Refinery?"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 42425.0,
      "end_time": 43641.0,
      "text": "So let’s check it out!"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 45925.0,
      "end_time": 48525.0,
      "text": "Let me introduce my friend here Mr. Hong"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 48875.0,
      "end_time": 50283.0,
      "text": "and Section Manager Xiao"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 50375.0,
      "end_time": 51800.0,
      "text": "Hi, Mr. Hong. (Hello)"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 51800.0,
      "end_time": 53275.0,
      "text": "Hi, Xiao Section Manager. (Hello)"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 53400.0,
      "end_time": 54375.0,
      "text": "Hello everyone."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 54575.0,
      "end_time": 57200.0,
      "text": "Bei-an, let me take you on a tour. (Alright)"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 59850.0,
      "end_time": 63350.0,
      "text": "We know that sugar was the most important product of Taiwan,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 63650.0,
      "end_time": 66350.0,
      "text": "so what’s the reason that sugar refinery"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 66350.0,
      "end_time": 68225.0,
      "text": "would be constructed in Shanhua?"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 68550.0,
      "end_time": 70725.0,
      "text": "Why the sugar refinery is located in Shanhua"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 70900.0,
      "end_time": 72000.0,
      "text": "can actually be explained like this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 72300.0,
      "end_time": 72896.0,
      "text": "first of all,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 73225.0,
      "end_time": 76607.0,
      "text": "because this factory was established in 1904."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 76875.0,
      "end_time": 78875.0,
      "text": "1904 is 8 years before the Republic of China,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 79900.0,
      "end_time": 85862.0,
      "text": "and that is 114 years of history."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 86396.0,
      "end_time": 91700.0,
      "text": "The sugar industry has a 400 year history of development in Taiwan."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 91850.0,
      "end_time": 96714.0,
      "text": "When establishing a sugar refinery, one must consider water sources."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 96950.0,
      "end_time": 101425.0,
      "text": "The process of refining sugar requires large amounts of water."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 101625.0,
      "end_time": 105850.0,
      "text": "For ease of access, a sugar refinery must be near a river."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 106000.0,
      "end_time": 109690.0,
      "text": "Tsung-Yeh sugar refinery is close to Zengwun River,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 109750.0,
      "end_time": 113375.0,
      "text": "and the Xinying sugar refinery is close to Jishui River."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 113700.0,
      "end_time": 117732.0,
      "text": "The second thing to consider is the accessibility of materials."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 118250.0,
      "end_time": 121289.0,
      "text": "There needs to be a large crop of sugarcane provided"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 121400.0,
      "end_time": 123500.0,
      "text": "as material for making sugar."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 123900.0,
      "end_time": 128316.0,
      "text": "Third of all, it should be situated in a densely populated area."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 128725.0,
      "end_time": 131799.0,
      "text": "In the early days the Siraya Tribe included"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 131800.0,
      "end_time": 132700.0,
      "text": "Soulang (now Jiali District),"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 132850.0,
      "end_time": 134625.0,
      "text": "Madou (now Madou District), Xinkang (now Sinshih District),"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 134800.0,
      "end_time": 135900.0,
      "text": "and Backloun (now Shanhua District)."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 136750.0,
      "end_time": 138774.0,
      "text": "Shanhua was one of the four great communities,"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 139125.0,
      "end_time": 140400.0,
      "text": "and at the same time met"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 140400.0,
      "end_time": 143575.0,
      "text": "the three basic requirements for a sugar refinery:"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 143950.0,
      "end_time": 147225.0,
      "text": "close to a water source, materials are easy to get,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 147525.0,
      "end_time": 148942.0,
      "text": "and a supply of labor."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 149225.0,
      "end_time": 153525.0,
      "text": "That is the reason why a sugar refinery was established in Shanhua."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 153975.0,
      "end_time": 155600.0,
      "text": "All the people like the sugar,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 155600.0,
      "end_time": 158150.0,
      "text": "and we can’t live without the sugar now,"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 158500.0,
      "end_time": 161325.0,
      "text": "so I want to ask for everyone that"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 161325.0,
      "end_time": 162799.0,
      "text": "how to make sugar？"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 163150.0,
      "end_time": 165582.0,
      "text": "Sugar is made from sugarcanes."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 165750.0,
      "end_time": 167478.0,
      "text": "Sugarcanes are harvested on farms"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 167478.0,
      "end_time": 170230.0,
      "text": "by machines and by hand."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 170486.0,
      "end_time": 172875.0,
      "text": "It is a bit more efficient to use machines."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 172975.0,
      "end_time": 176751.0,
      "text": "Sugar refineries used to transport sugarcanes by railroads."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 177325.0,
      "end_time": 179436.0,
      "text": "Now we use trucks to transport them."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 179900.0,
      "end_time": 183500.0,
      "text": "After the raw materials have been delivered to the refinery,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 183925.0,
      "end_time": 187317.0,
      "text": "the sugarcanes are first pressed for juices in the pressing room."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 187775.0,
      "end_time": 191198.0,
      "text": "The sugarcane chaff is then used as fuel in the boiler room."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 191750.0,
      "end_time": 195325.0,
      "text": "At the same time, the sugarcane juice is sent to the cleaning room"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 195600.0,
      "end_time": 197904.0,
      "text": "to be sterilized through high temperatures."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 198250.0,
      "end_time": 201578.0,
      "text": "After the process, the moisture is evaporated"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 201850.0,
      "end_time": 205490.0,
      "text": "and the concentrate can be made into sugar crystals."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 205325.0,
      "end_time": 208774.0,
      "text": "When the concentrations levels are around 64 percent,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 209250.0,
      "end_time": 211275.0,
      "text": "it is sent to the crystallization room."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 211700.0,
      "end_time": 215524.0,
      "text": "In the process of crystallization, molasses will be produced,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 215925.0,
      "end_time": 219971.0,
      "text": "so once again the sugar is sent to a molasses separation room."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 220350.0,
      "end_time": 223200.0,
      "text": "Using high pressure and centrifugal force"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 223475.0,
      "end_time": 226000.0,
      "text": "molasses is separated from sugar."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 226250.0,
      "end_time": 230250.0,
      "text": "Molasses can then be made into monosodium glutamate(MSG)."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 230150.0,
      "end_time": 233550.0,
      "text": "Nowadays, molasses is used as fertilizer."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 233700.0,
      "end_time": 237796.0,
      "text": "The finished sugar product is sent to be packaged in the packaging room."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 239375.0,
      "end_time": 242575.0,
      "text": "So can you show us around the heritage museum"
    },
    {
